[{"Id": 1014414, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Allamah Majlisi (r) writes in Behaar al-Anwaar: Recite farewell Ziyarat which has been narrated by Imam Ja’far al-Sadiq (a) which he (a) had recited while departing from the Holy Prophet (s). The narration of Allamah Majlisi (r) does not indicate that this farewell Ziyarat is for particular infallible. When you intend to leave and bid farewell to the Imam, you may recite farewell ziyarat in the following words...", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Allamah Majlisi (r) ne Behaarul Anwaar mein naql kiya hai keh: Ziyarat’e Wida padho keh jo Imam Jafar As-Sadiq (a) ne Rasool’e Khuda (s) se rukhsat hote waqt padhi thi. Allamah Majlisi ki yeh riwaayat saabit nahin karti hai keh yeh kisi khaas maasoom (a) ke liye hai. Jab tum Imam (a) se aakhri rukhsati lena chaho to ziyarat’e wida in alfaazo’n mein adaa karo…", "UrduDescription": "علامہ مجلسی نے بحار الانوا میں نقل کیا ہے کہ: زیارتِ وداع پڑھوں کہ جو امام جعفر صادقؑ نے رسولِ خداؐ سے رخصت ہوتے وقت پڑھی تھی۔ علامی مجلسی کی یہ روایت ثابت نہیں کرتی ہے کہ یہ کسی خاص معصومؑ کے لئے ہے۔ جب تم امامؑ سے آخری رخصت لینا چاہو تو زیارتِ وداع ان الفاظوں میں ادا کرو۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "Arabi